<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="81" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="81">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="81">
<taxonomicName genus="H." lsidName="H. albiflora" pageId="2" pageNumber="81" rank="species" species="albiflora">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="81">H. albiflora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differs significantly from 
<taxonomicName genus="H." lsidName="H. gamosepala" pageId="2" pageNumber="81" rank="species" species="gamosepala">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="81">H. gamosepala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by its 5-parted calyx from the base (vs. 5-lobed from middle), longer peduncle, 3-6 cm (vs. 0.2-0.4 cm), white corolla (vs. pink corolla) and longer pistil, 2-2.5 cm (vs. ~ 1.5 cm). After extensive observations, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="X. G. Xiang, Z. Y. Guo &amp; Z. W. Wu" authorityYear="2019" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Hemiboea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Hemiboea albiflora" order="Lamiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="81" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="albiflora">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="81">Hemiboea albiflora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is close to 
<taxonomicName genus="H." infraspecific-rank="var." lsidName="H. cavaleriei var. paucinervis" pageId="2" pageNumber="81" rank="variety" species="cavaleriei" variety="paucinervis">H. cavaleriei var. paucinervis</taxonomicName>
W. T. Wang et Z. Y. Li and 
<taxonomicName genus="H." lsidName="H. subcapitata" pageId="2" pageNumber="81" rank="species" species="subcapitata">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="81">H. subcapitata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
C.B. Clarke, but differs from them through its longer petiole, 3-6 cm; larger involucre, 2-3 cm in diameter; white corolla, glabrous outside; and longer staminal filaments, 1.8-2 cm long. The detailed morphological comparisons are listed in Table 
<tableCitation captionStart="Table 1" captionStartId="T1" captionText="Table 1. Morphological comparisons between H. albiflora and the similar species H. gamosepala, H. cavaleriei var. paucinervis and H. subcapitata." httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/02E0871E80512CCA2B6838B7E0E803EB" pageId="2" pageNumber="81" tableUuid="02E0871E80512CCA2B6838B7E0E803EB">1</tableCitation>
.
</paragraph>
